From 8f56fa937d7b6e7e85802b3418594cdc54b36118 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Pavankumar Nandeshwar <quic_pnandesh@quicinc.com>
Date: Thu, 27 Mar 2025 09:54:41 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] wifi: ath12k: Build all the files in wifi7 directory into
 ath12k_wifi7.ko

Move all the files which were built as part of ath12k.ko but existed in
wifi7 directory to ath12k_wifi7.ko. Make neccessary symbol exports
from ath12k.ko and remove symbol exports from wifi7 directory as
they will not be needed anymore.

Signed-off-by: Pavankumar Nandeshwar <quic_pnandesh@quicinc.com>
